==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Zephyrus
<hw>Zeph"y*rus</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L. See
<er>Zephyr</er>.]</ety> <def>The west wind, or zephyr; -- usually
personified, and made the most mild and gentle of all the sylvan
deities.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Mild as when <qex>Zephyrus</qex> on Flora breathes.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Zeppelin</ent>⟦br⟧
